pageProduct.name: U by Kotex Sport Ultrathins Pads Regular Wing 12 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

U by Kotex® Sport Ultrathins are specifically designed to offer period protection while you're working out. The super-absorbent Flexfit* Core moulds to your body, providing protection against leaks even during your most vigorous workout or challenging Pilates class. So now you can forget your pad and just concentrate on your workout.

  • Moves-With-You Protection specifically designed to protect you while you're working out. With a super-absorbent FLEXFIT* Core they are shaped to mould to your body as you move
  • Breathable, quick dry cover to leave you feeling dry and fresh
  • With wings to help keep your pad in place, especially during vigorous workouts
  • Super thin and soft design for the ultimate in comfort
  • Perfect for medium flow days during the day.

Boxed Contents: 12 Regular Pads

Size: 12 Pads

Gender: Female

Directions

Remove wrapper and peel strip in one quick move

STORAGE AND DISPOSAL

This packaging is recyclable in Australia through the REDcycle Program. To find your nearest drop off location, visit www.redcycle.net.au. Recycle empty bags with carrier bags at leading retailers. Not at kerbside. For more information visit www.kimberly-clark.com.au/en/sustainability
